title: [FSX/P3D] B.Renk - MyTraffic Professional 6.0
description:
MyTRAFFIC 6

The latest technology of AI Traffic for FSX and Prepar3D!

Supported simulators are Microsoft Flight Simulator X, Microsoft Flight Simulator X Steam Edition, Prepar3D Version 1 (1.4 recommended), Prepar3D Version 2 (up to version 2.5).

Based on award winning MyTraffic 5, the leading AI traffic program for FSX, this new build is largely reorganized for simultaneous support of various simulators. 
All included airports and schedules have been rebuild for the needs of Prepar3D V2.3 and above. 
Ihe included aircraft types are in the highly optimized FSX Service Pack 2 format, pairing top optical quality with ultimate performance
